quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,102,"∆Āe nanoytaa wuu…óaango magge kam…ďe hi…ďe e nder ko wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin lokaa(woo…óa) kon, ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe"
  21,103,"Suninoytaa…ďe …óen∆īere mawnde nden, Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen no ja…ď…ďoo…ďe […ďe wi'a:] \"Ko ndee woni √Ďalaande mo'on, nden nde laatino…óon hi…óon fodee"
  21,104,"√Ďalnde Men taggoyta kammu ngun wano taggugol …óerol defte. Ko wano Men fu…ó…óori non ka arannde tagu Men ruttirta ngu, […óum] ko Fodoore e dow Amen, pellet, Menen Men laatike golloo…ďe"
  21,105,"Gom…óii Men winndiino ka Jabuura …ďaawo Alluwal Reenaangal ngal, pellet, leydi ndin ko jeyaa…ďe Am mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen ronoyta ndi"
  21,106,"Pellet,no e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] jottingol wonannde yim…ďe rewoo…ďe …ďen"
  21,107,Men Nuliraali ma si wanaa Yurmeende wonannde winndire nden
  21,108,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am, wonndema Rewetee…óo mon On ko O Rewetee…óo Gooto. Enee, hara onon ko on jebbilii…ďe?\". @Corrected"
  21,109,"Si tawii …ďe …óurnike, maaku: \"Mi anndinii on e dow fotondiral, pellet, mi anndaa si no …ďadii maa…óum si no wo…ó…ói kon ko foda…óon"
  21,110,"Pellet, Kanko hiMo Anndi ko fee√Īi kon e konngol ngol, hiMo Anndi kadi ko suu…óoton"
  21,111,"Mi anndaa non, belejo'o …óum ko jarrabuyee mo'on, e dakamme haa e dummunne"
  21,112,"Maaku: \"Jooma, √Ďaawir Goonga kan ko Joomi amen Hinnorante On woni Wallitortee…óo On e dow kon ko sifoto…óon"
